Earring's ``Radar Love,'' from Dave Dudley's ``Six Days on the
Road'' to Duane Eddy's ``Forty Miles of Bad Road'' to Robert
Mitchum's ``Ballad of Thunder Road.''
</P>
<P>
   It features an invitation from TV's Dinah Shore to ``See the
