ever hit the ground, and Jimmie designed it.
</P>
<P>
   ``I'd go to him for design advice, and he would say, `James, I
go for traditional, traditional, traditional. Keep it simple, you
can't go wrong.' Same with his music. Each note is played with such
feeling. With his cars, his designs may seem simple on the surface,
