machines turning out New York guidebooks is the city itself. But
here's a word of advice: When shopping for a guide, do not be
fooled by the 1999 on the cover, or copyright date. Most guides are
researched more than a year in advance.
</P>
<P>
   WITH: TRAVEL BRIEFS: The next Olympic Summer Games, to be held
in Sydney, are a little less than 18 months away, but it's not too
early to order hotel accommodations and tickets.
