   (PAGE INCLUDES 3 COLOR PHOTOGRAPHS)
</P>
<P>
   BETTER BREAST ENHANCER?: A Brazilian doctor has created a new
procedure that involves an ``internal brassiere'' formed of mesh.
It's one of the hottest techniques in the plastic-surgery business,
where breast reshaping, reduction and reconstruction take center
stage. (Includes a 4-column color photograph of a doctor inserting
a mesh into a woman's breast and a 2-column color photo of an
