State, a surprise Final Four team in the NCAA tournament. O'Brien
will go up against Connecticut's Jim Calhoun on Saturday, and
Calhoun has beaten O'Brien the last 18 times they coached against
each other. By Judy Battista.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-OREGON-SMITH (Undated) _ Feature on Akili Smith, the Oregon
quarterback who is suddenly moving up on the NFL draft charts and
could even be the surprising No. 1 pick in April. By Thomas George.
