<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-KOSOVO-UPDATE-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   (adds KOSOVO-PRIMAKOV, KOSOVO-MILITARY-ASSESS, KOSOVO-BELGRADE
and KOSOVO-MILOSEVIC; deletes KOSOVO-ASSESS, KOSOVO-MILITARY and
