   ``I hear the wine. It's like a structure. I see it as a piece. I
hear it before I taste it. It's calling me. And then I start to
hear it when I'm tasting it. Not that I put crystal suppositories
up my a_. ... I'm not New Age.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Tori Amos explaining her passion for wine, in Wine X, a
magazine that seems aimed at young wine-lovers.
