   TOP
</P>
<P>
   Lead stories:
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-RDP (Washington) _ NATO is poised to begin air strikes as
President Clinton declares that force is necessary to halt the
aggression of the Serbs against ethnic Albanians in the province of
Kosovo. By Jane Perlez. (We plan to move the story by 8:30 p.m. ET
in ``i'' news file.)
</P>
<P>
   The stories run under a 4-column, 2-line hed.
</P>
<P>
   With photos and locator map.
</P>
<P>
   Top center: 3-column photo.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-MILITARY-ASSESS (Brussels, Belgium) _ Initial NATO
