soon.
</P>
<P>
   By Jim Moore. (Story will move in the ``s'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   BKN-SONICS (Seattle) _ The Sonics were busy on the transaction
front Tuesday, signing free agent guard John Crotty (released by
the Trail Blazers) and releasing Moochie Norris (on the injured
list with insomnia). The team put Vin Baker (injured thumb
ligaments) on the injured list, but say they have no immediate
plans to sign a replacement.
</P>
<P>
   By Ronald Tillery. (Story will move in the ``s'' category.)
</P>
<P>
   BKN-THIEL-COLUMN (Seattle) _ The good news about the Vin Baker
thumb injury is that it happened to his eating hand. The team, at
this point, actually might be better off without him. A look at the
Sonics' plight and prospects the rest of the season.
</P>
<P>
   By Art Thiel. (Story will move in the ``s'' category.)
</P>
