<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Wednesday, Mar.
17, about software robots misspelled the given name of the Czech
dramatist who wrote the play ``R.U.R.'' and misstated the year in
which it was first produced. The playwright was Karel Capek, not
Karl, and the production was in 1921, not 1917.
