</P>
<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-ANALYSIS (London) _ Many observers expect Serbian troops
already sweeping through northern Kosovo to react to NATO
airstrikes with wholesale slaughter. Will NATO try to stop that? By
Kevin Cullen. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
