   KOSOVO-CLINTON (Washington) _ Clinton rallies Congress to
support attack on Serbs. US officials warn Belgrade that airstrikes
would be swift and painful following Milosevic's refusal to budge.
Russian Prime Minister Yevgeny Primakov cancels trip to US in
midflight. By Ann Scales and Louise Palmer. 1300 words.
